data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET Welcome home to this fabulous ranch in sought after East Cobb neighborhood. Upon entering the home you will be greated by two story, large family room, with beautiful fireplace. Separate dining room can be used as an office as well. Kitchen was updated with white cabinets, beautful granite countertops, large island and a sliding door overlooking amazing patio and professionally landscaped backyard. An open and bright living space and dining room are perfect for entertaining with family and friends. All bedrooms are generous sizes. Master suite features view to the erene backyard, vaulted ceiling and large walkin closet. Hardwood floors and fresh neutral paint. Multi-level backyard to enjoy with your family and friends. This swim/tennis community is conveniently located close to a wide range of amenities, including shopping centers, restaurants and parks.
